ces were between $1.11 and $3.59, with an estimated average price of $2.13. The stock is now traded at around $0.74. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 2.84%. The holdings were 5,202,967 shares as of 2017-03-31.Added: ReneSola Ltd (SOL)Shah Capital Management added to the holdings in ReneSola Ltd by 27.82%. The purchase prices were between $2.26 and $3.48, with an estimated average price of $2.91. The stock is now traded at around $2.44. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was less than 0.01%. The holdings were 1,874,122 shares as of 2017-03-31.Sold Out: Coeur Mining Inc (CDE)Shah Capital Management sold out the holdings in Coeur Mining Inc. The sale prices were between $7.33 and $12.02, with an estimated average price of $9.54.Sold Out: Petroleo Brasileiro SA Petrobras (PBR)Shah Capital Management sold out the holdings in Petroleo Brasileiro SA Petrobras. The sale prices were between $8.81 and $11.54, with an estimated average price of $10.27.Sold Out: Mobile TeleSystems PJSC (MBT)Shah Capital Management sold out the holdings in Mobile TeleSystems PJSC. The sale prices were between $9.28 and $11.51, with an estimated average price of $10.38.Sold Out: China Unicom (Hong Kong) Ltd (CHU)Shah Capital Management sold out the holdings in China Unicom (Hong Kong) Ltd. The sale prices were between $11.3 and $13.52, with an estimated average price of $12.21.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 3 Warning Signs with SDRL. Click here to check it out.SDRL 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of SDRLPeter Lynch Chart of SDRLPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



