Shah CapitalShah Capital is an investment firm that provides portfolio management services to high net-worth individuals and institutional investors.
Shah Capital is a global investment firm targeting unique opportunities 
primarily focusing on deep value, turn-around and special situations










Our Team - Shah Capital






































Shah CapitalShah Capital is an investment firm that provides portfolio management services to high net-worth individuals and institutional investors.


 Our Team
Just like most successful companies, it’s people are the root for success. 
At Shah Capital, our team compromises a group of individuals with diverse
backgrounds and global experience. As a firm, we stay intensely focused and
don’t get distracted by what we deem as “noise” or a lot of irrelevant information.

